data.description: Step into luxury and convenience at 1016 Southern Avenue SE, the epitome of elegance in Washington DC. This stunning home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 2 half baths, and a fully finished basement. No more circling the block for parking, you’ll always have 2 designated spots waiting for you that leads to a beautiful backyard. Prepare to be enchanted by the beautiful kitchen with its modern design where every meal will be a delight. It's not just the interior that will leave you captivated, location is everything. Just 2 blocks away from the Southern Avenue Metro Station making commuting is a breeze, minutes away from the vibrant National Harbor with endless entertainment and dining, easy access to major highways like the Interstate 495 and Interstate 295. Whether you're heading to work or exploring the wonders of Washington DC your journey will be seamless. The perks don't stop there. This home is perfectly situated within minutes of entertainment districts such as Capitol Hill Marine Barracks, Eastern Market, the Navy Yard, Andrews Air Force Base and all of Washington's connecting DMV.
